Title: Computers are Pretty Cool.
Author: Patrick Murrell
Content: Computers, they are pretty cool aren't they?. You can visit websites with them, make calculations, talk to your friends, play games, and get work done on them. I like computers.

Title: Computers Suck!.
Author: Matrick Purrell
Content: Computers are the worst! They are so slow, I just want to print a recipie out and I can't print! Ugh, I hate computers!

Title: Making a website
Author: Patrick Murrell
Content: Making websites is pretty easy. I made this one pretty quickly. So there's that.

Title: Tests
Author: Patrick Murrell
Content: Taking tests is pretty hard. You need to study for them to get a good grade.
